  "description": {
    "zh": "你最近几个任务都很可靠，所以我想你现在可以接一个更有趣的工作了。我需要为清理小队测试一些装备——特别是主动式耳机。不同品牌的。\n\n干掉一些当地渣滓或操作员，无论你遇到谁，我相信你很容易就能找到麻烦——毕竟你就像块磁铁。在你做这件事的时候使用这些耳机，找出它们在战斗中的表现如何，毕竟我不能给我的人廉价的听力保护。用完后把耳机带回来给我，别指望我送你礼物，我的哥们。",
    "en": "You were reliable with the last few tasks so I guess you can get a more interesting job now. I need a bit of gear tested for the cleanup crew - Active headsets, to be specific. Different brands.\n\nShoot down some local scum or operators, whoever you cross paths with, I'm sure you can find trouble easily - After all you are like a magnet for that. Use these headsets while you do it and find out how well they work in combat, I can't give my guys cheap hearing protection after all. Bring me back the headsets when you're done, don't expect any gifts from me my guy."
  },
